    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/s-4hana-2025-gcts-synchronous-push-issue-with-gitlab-repository/qaq-p/14323148</id>
    <title>S/4HANA 2025: gCTS 'Synchronous Push' issue with GitLab repository</title>
    <updated>2026-02-06T16:19:08.350000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>alfonso_onapsis</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/752370</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;I configured gCTS with a &lt;STRONG&gt;GitLab&lt;/STRONG&gt; repository in an SAP S/4HANA &lt;STRONG&gt;2025&lt;/STRONG&gt; environment. While commits work correctly upon releasing the transports, I have encountered an issue with the 'Push Objects' functionality during synchronous execution.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="alfonso_onapsis_0-1770389165425.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/369620iA1726BF5B6BC64C8/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="alfonso_onapsis_0-1770389165425.png" alt="alfonso_onapsis_0-1770389165425.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="alfonso_onapsis_1-1770389288830.png" style="width: 216px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/369622i890863C812559E10/image-dimensions/216x152?v=v2" width="216" height="152" role="button" title="alfonso_onapsis_1-1770389288830.png" alt="alfonso_onapsis_1-1770389288830.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Debugging the point of failure reveals that the exception occurs because the system cannot identify the API user.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="alfonso_onapsis_2-1770389465563.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/369625i44F277CAC1BD6726/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="alfonso_onapsis_2-1770389465563.png" alt="alfonso_onapsis_2-1770389465563.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Comparing this method with gCTS in S/4HANA &lt;STRONG&gt;2023&lt;/STRONG&gt;, I noticed that the API object is only instantiated when using &lt;STRONG&gt;GitHub&lt;/STRONG&gt;. Since I am using &lt;STRONG&gt;GitLab&lt;/STRONG&gt;, the code to retrieve the API object is bypassed, which is why 'Synchronous Push Object' works correctly in that version.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="alfonso_onapsis_3-1770389855469.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/369628iB4A9096DC7BF6801/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="alfonso_onapsis_3-1770389855469.png" alt="alfonso_onapsis_3-1770389855469.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Is anyone else experiencing this error using gCTS on S/4HANA &lt;STRONG&gt;2025&lt;/STRONG&gt; + &lt;STRONG&gt;GitLab&lt;/STRONG&gt; during a 'Synchronous Push Object'? If you're using gCTS on S/4HANA &lt;STRONG&gt;2025 &lt;/STRONG&gt;+&lt;STRONG&gt;GitHub&lt;/STRONG&gt; instead, I’d appreciate your feedback to confirm if the functionality works in that setup.&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;Thank you,&lt;BR /&gt;Alfonso.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/technology-q-a/s-4hana-2025-gcts-synchronous-push-issue-with-gitlab-repository/qaq-p/14323148"/>
    <published>2026-02-06T16:19:08.350000+01:00</published>
  </entry>
